snippet.title: The Odyssey | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Odyssey - In Theaters 07.17.26

Christopher Nolan‚Äôs next film, The Odyssey, is a mythic action epic shot across the world using brand new IMAX¬Æ film technology. The film brings Homer‚Äôs foundational saga to IMAX¬Æ film screens for the first time and opens in theaters everywhere on July 17, 2026. 

The Odyssey stars Matt Damon, Tom Holland, Anne Hathaway, Robert Pattinson and Lupita Nyong‚Äôo, with Zendaya and Charlize Theron.

The Odyssey is produced by Emma Thomas and Christopher Nolan for their company, Syncopy. The executive producer is Thomas Hayslip.

snippet.title: Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Whatever happened to Tommy Shelby, the famous gypsy gangster? Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man premieres March 6 in select cinemas and March 20 2026 on Netflix.

snippet.title: YABI - BOOMERANG ( OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO )
snippet.description:

Recorded at: Kadak Nepali
Prod. By: Rick Anthony
Mixed & Mastered by: Ruthlexx
Mixtape: Bommerang
Directed: Samirvision

Boomerang is a raw and emotional record that comes back harder every time just like the feelings it carries.This track dives into love, pain, and the moments you can‚Äôt escape no matter how far you run.Recorded at Kadak Nepali and mixed & mastered by Ruthlexx, Boomerang brings heavy energy with a polished sound.

snippet.title: Yabesh Thapa - Shital | OFFICIAL VISUALIZER
snippet.description:
Shital is the second song from the album 'GhaamChhaya' and is a very emotional song for me. It talks about how love would have been different if they had more time. In the end we all turn to dust. Only if he had the power to compel gods to freeze time in place, the story would have a different outcome.

Written, Composed, Produced and Performed by Yabesh Thapa
Recorded, Mixed and Mastered by Kobid Bazra
Recorded at Bazra Creation Records

Visuals by Noisy

Buy the album 'GhaamChhaya' 
https://classxpresentation.com/global/shop/product/ghaam-chhaya

snippet.description:
‚Äî Attention Viewers ‚ö†Ô∏è
‚Äî This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
‚Äî Avengers: Doomsday - Steve Rogers Will Return

‚Äî Music Credits - https://youtu.be/6Ot-gRruxng

‚Äî This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support ‚Äî now let‚Äôs dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. üé¨‚ú®

‚Äî In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story centers on the long-unresolved consequences of Steve Rogers‚Äô final choice in Endgame, revealing that his decision to remain in the past fractured reality in ways the Avengers never anticipated. As timelines splinter and the stability of the main MCU begins to erode, Steve is forced back into the conflict, confronting the personal cost of his legacy and the ripple effects of his sacrifice. The narrative hints at a corrupted alternate reality where familiar heroes took darker paths, drawing Doctor Doom into the heart of the multiversal crisis and threatening total collapse across worlds. With time itself no longer trustworthy, Rogers emerges as both the cause and the possible solution, facing a reckoning that could determine whether the prime timeline survives or is rewritten forever.

The fate of this weary soul is truly unfortunate,
The fate of this troubled heart is unfortunate.
Love was never written in my destiny,
Oh, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,
Indeed, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate.

A heart slashed by sharp, bitter words,
No cure is found- it keeps aching endlessly.
Wherever I go, I earn no respect,
When my own fate is flawed, whom can I blame?
Oh, the fate of this poor soul is unfortunate,
The fate of this poor soul is unfortunate.
Love was never written in my destiny,
Oh, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,
Indeed, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate.

This helpless life keeps giving me pain,
Even the little laughter I find takes away.
Where can this restless heart find peace?
Even when tears fall, I walk smiling - day and night.
The fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,
The fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,
Love was never written in my destiny,
Oh, the fate of this weary soul is unfortunate,

snippet.title: [NP] 2025 PUBG MOBILE STAR CHALLENGE NEPAL | AUCTION DAY
snippet.description:
Support My Channel Thru :
Channel Membership : https://www.youtube.com/c/AnshYT/join
or
Super Chat : https://cr8.rs/@AnshYT
--------------------------------------------------------------
AUCTION DAY is here for the 2025 PUBG MOBILE STAR CHALLENGE NEPAL!

16 creators go head-to-head in a live bidding war, each starting with 5,000 Star Coins to sign 3‚Äì4 players and form their ultimate squad for the Grand Finals.
Prize Pool: $5,000
Match Days: 26/12/2025 ‚Äì 28/12/2025 (3 match days, 5 matches per team, 16 total teams)

Invited PUBGM creators: Ansh YT, Cr7 Horaa, Suku FB, Joker Plays, T2K Rulz, Killer YT, Delta, Rashmay, Ritika Slays, MafiaNinja

Special non‚ÄëPUBGM creators: Gulshan Kumar Jha, Sushant Khatri, Samir Shrestha, Mr. Junior, Rachana Dahal, Alish Rai

What‚Äôs happening today?
- 16 creators receive 5,000 Star Coins each
- Live auction to pick 3‚Äì4 players per creator
- Star-studded squads get locked in for the Grand Finals action on 26‚Äì28 Dec

Watch the full auction LIVE and see who builds the strongest roster for the battlegrounds!

#PUBGMobile #PMSC2025 #StarChallenge #NepalEsports #AuctionDay #PUBGMobileEsports

snippet.title: Bhool | Swar | Lyrics Visualiser
snippet.description:
We composed this song while on a plane during our tour to Australia, and we hope you enjoy it, even as a lyrical video.
Thank you for all your love and support. 


‚ÄúBhool‚Äù speaks of that quiet realization, when loving someone no longer feels worthy of the complete love you gave.

snippet.description:
Orginal Verson Of This song 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kYEVMceFIrE

Bandipur Jaula Sangai Basaula ( ‡§¨‡§®‡•ç‡§¶‡•Ä‡§™‡•Å‡§∞ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡§æ ‡§∏‡§Å‡§ó‡•à ‡§¨‡§∏‡•å‡§≤‡§æ ) is a beautiful Presentation of @JibihangRaiOfficial in associated with HANGKIM RECORDS. snippet.title: Arjun Katuwal - Teri Meri Kahani (Official Music Video) Nimesh Shrestha || Barsha kshetri || Vague
snippet.description:
This song is a humble tribute to the beautiful but heartbreaking love story of Bibek Pangeni and Srijana Subedi, a couple who showed the world what true love, courage, and devotion really look like.
Their journey reminded us that love is not just about the smiles we share, but also the battles we fight together, hand in hand.
It is our way of honoring a love that touched millions and continues to inspire people everywhere.

To Bibek, your strength and smile will never be forgotten.
To Srijana, your love and dedication remain a timeless example of what it means to stand by someone with your whole heart.
And to everyone watching, may their story remind you to cherish the people you love a little more today.

Audio credits :
Music & Production: Arjun Katuwal
Asst Music producer: Bibas Music (FREQ Temple)
Lyrics: Ritik Koul (Vague)
Mix & Master : Pukhraj Sonkar(inhouse studio)
Violins : Krishna Raj
Strings Orchestrated : Rakesh Venkatapuram
Flute : Swarnim Maharjan

snippet.title: Shinchan and Franklin  Celebrate Christmas with Santa Claus in GTA 5
snippet.description:
In this video Shinchan and Franklin  Celebrate Christmas with Santa Claus in GTA 5

In this fun and festive GTA 5 story mod, Franklin transforms his house into a Christmas wonderland, decorating it with sparkling lights and a massive Christmas tree. üåü

Franklin wants to spread joy to all his gang members, so he goes on a gift-hunting adventure! First, he surprises Shinchan with an amazing 3-wheeled blue bike, then grabs a super muscle car equipped with an RPG rocket launcher! üöóüí• But the holiday fun doesn‚Äôt stop there ‚Äî Franklin also buys delicious cake and wine for everyone in the gang. üéÇüç∑

Things get magical when Franklin meets Santa Claus on his rooftop! üéÖ Santa tells him about his second sleigh, parked near the Los Santos Dam Observatory. Franklin sets off on a mission to find this beautiful sleigh and bring it home.

Finally, it‚Äôs time for the big celebration! Franklin wakes up the gang, hands out all the gifts, and invites Chop and Shinchan for a thrilling ride on the sleigh. Together, they soar across the Los Santos skyline, enjoying the festive spirit and the joy of friendship. ‚ú®

Don‚Äôt miss this epic Christmas story full of laughter, surprises, and GTA 5 chaos!

snippet.description:
#tukimusic  #pokhara #nephop 
TUKI MUSIC - Arajak (‡§Ö‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§ï)


"Arajak (‡§Ö‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§ï)" is a revolutionary song that captures the emotional turmoil relating to death of ‚ÄúGen Z ‚Äú protesters in Nepal. On 9 September 2025, protesters angered by government repression and corruption stormed the Nepalese Federal Parliament Building in Kathmandu. The protest escalated when the police killed 19 protesters including a 12-year-old child on 8 September 2025. Through this evocative lyrics and soulful melody, the song portrays frustration of Nepalese Youth towards corruption and political insanity.

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - INAAM (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
The 15th studio recorded single - Inaam, written, sung and composed by #AnuvJain is here!

Listen to 'Inaam' on all streaming platforms : https://UMGI.lnk.to/Inaam_AnuvJain


Audio Credits: 

Artist: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Composer: Anuv Jain (@anuvjain)
Producer: Lost Stories (@loststories)
Guitars: Keba Jeremiah (@kebajr)
Choirs: Solomon Konwar (@eskay______) Prachi Kapil (@prachi.kapil8)
Mix Engineers: Rishab Joshi (@rishabjoshi) & Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Master Engineer: Mukul Jain (@mixbymukul)
Recording Engineer: Jay Rana (@itsjayrana)
Additional Programming: Sarthak Kalyani (@sarthak.kalyani)
Dolby Atmos Mastered at Ferris Wheel Studios (@ferriswheelstudios)

Video Credits: 

Director: Bhagyesh Rajeshirke (@bhagyesh_rajeshirke)
Associate Director: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Creative Director: Pranjal Asha (@pranjalasha)
Editor: Manthan Sharma (@manthan.mp4)
Producer: Arnab Kar (@arnab_kar)

Management: REPRESENT
Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‚ÄòInaam‚Äô the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

Jeete jabse ho

Wah wah

Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan

Khush na kahin se

Hum janey tumko

Shayad galat the

Har woh inaam
